  "Text": "文本规则：严格遵循约束规则。仅返回翻译字符串输出，不要包含任何解释、介绍或周围标记。保留所有消息占位符令牌如{name}或{count}不变。\n\nText: 严格规则：请参阅详细信息以了解有关如何维护数据库一致性的更多信息。",
  "Text Statistics": "文本统计",
  "Text columns only": "文本列仅限使用",
  "Text copied to clipboard": "文本已复制到剪贴板",
  "The Dashboard and Health Score above are live previews. Browse every tool below, grouped by what it does — some need your app running with the Drift debug server connected.": "上述仪表板和健康评分是实时预览。请浏览下方的每个工具，它们按功能分组——有些需要您的应用在连接Drift调试服务器的情况下运行。",
  "The baseline snapshot to compare from": "用于比较的基础快照",
  "The connected Drift debug server has its monitoring kill switch engaged (it may have started dormant), so data requests will be refused until it is resumed.": "连接的Drift调试服务器启用了监控关闭开关（可能处于休眠状态），因此在此之前数据请求将被拒绝。",
  "The debug server exposes your whole database, so by default it binds to 127.0.0.1 (loopback) only — reachable from this machine, not from any other host on your network. To reach it from a physical device by its LAN IP, start it with loopbackOnly: false and set an authToken.": "调试服务器会暴露您的整个数据库，因此默认情况下它仅绑定到本地回环地址 127.0.0.1 — 只可以从本机访问，而不能从网络上的其他主机访问。要在其局域网 IP 地址上从物理设备访问它，请使用 loopbackOnly: false 并设置一个 authToken。",
  "The emulator runs in a separate network namespace. The extension automatically tries adb forward when a debug session starts, but you can also do it manually:": "模拟器运行在单独的网络命名空间中。扩展会在调试会话开始时自动尝试adb转发，但您也可以手动进行：",
  "The extension is connected to your app and serving live data.": "该扩展已连接到您的应用并提供实时数据。",
  "The extension uses two connection methods:": "该扩展使用两种连接方法：",
  "The global kill switch is engaged — nothing is recorded and data endpoints answer 403.": "全局紧急切换已激活——不记录任何数据且数据端点返回403错误。",
  "The global kill switch is engaged: no query recording, no diagnostics, no background sweeps. Data endpoints on the Drift debug server answer 403 until monitoring is resumed.": "全局终止开关已启用：不记录查询、不进行诊断、不进行后台扫描。Drift debug server的数据端点在恢复监控之前将返回403。",
  "The server may not be ready yet; try <strong>Retry Connection</strong> after a few seconds": "服务器可能尚未就绪；几秒后尝试<strong>重试连接</strong>",
  "The sidebar remembered your database structure from the last connection and is showing it from a workspace cache. Table and column names are real, but there is no live data and the row counts are stale. Reconnect to the running app to load live data.": "侧边栏记住了上次连接时的数据库结构，并从工作区缓存中显示。表和列名是真实的，但没有实时数据且行数已过时。请重新连接运行中的应用以加载实时数据。",
  "The target snapshot to compare against": "与比较的目标快照",
